Amazon Customer
5 3
Not even close to advertised pictures
I'll start by saying they just glide onto your lips and make them feel really soft. They leave more of an oily or wet feeling similar to lip oil. They come in a twist up case and are easy to apply. The cap stays on secure after snapping it in place so it won't pop off easily in your bag. They don't have a taste or a bad smell which is a big plus. They didn't irritate my lips or the skin around them. The tint is actually the only part I have issue with. I checked a swatch on my hand to see color. I used the darkest color which is labeled as black candy for my example. It showed a slight tint against my very light skin almost like a browser however when I applied it to my lips it didn't tint at all just left a slight shimmer. There's nothing wrong with that at all and it did look nice except it's labled as a tint and shows a big difference in color on the ad examples which you will not achieve no matter how heavily you apply it. They feel nice on your lips but if you're expecting anything even close to the advertised pictures you will be highly disappointed. For the price they're still a decent shimmer balm and can help moisturize and protect your lips.
